title: HUMAN EVENTS DAILY: NOV 15 2021 - KYLE RITTENHOUSE TRIAL IS ABOUT THE 2ND AMENDMENT
description:
On today’s episode of Human Events Daily, The Kyle Rittenhouse Trial is nearing the end and the prosecution has made the entire trial about the 2nd Amendment, CNN goes full White House Shade War regarding First Lady Jill Biden and VP Kamala Harris, the surge of illegal migrants at the Polish Border has been EXPOSED, and Pfizer CEO calls for criminalization of vaccine criticism. 


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
